        {
            "id": 6011084,
            "title": "臻鼎-KY 5月營收117億元刷新同期紀錄 IC載板動能強勁",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4958-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公布最新營收資訊，2025 年 5 月營收 117.91 億元，月減 13.23%、年增 10.83%，創歷年同期新高；累計今年 1-5 月營收 654.62 億元，年增 20.76%，也為同期新高，充分展現公司受惠於高階應用需求驅動下所展現的穩健成長實力。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011084%2Fl%2F2808bffb9d943a1a153aeb29c515a192.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">臻鼎-KY董事長沈慶芳。(圖：臻鼎提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎 - KY 表示，5 月營收維持雙位數年增，四大產品應用中以 IC 載板成長最高，年增逾 40% 並創下單月新高，其次為電腦消費及行動通訊。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎 - KY 指出，IC 載板業務接單動能強勁，預期今年 IC 載板仍將是成長最快的業務部門，可望年增超過 40%；同時，公司正全力推進在高雄 AI 園區建設，擴充高階 ABF 載板產能，待 2026 年產能開出後，將能承接國際一線客戶的先進封裝載板需求，進一步推升整體營運表現。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎 - KY2025 年第一季營收 400.82 億元，創同期新高，毛利率 14.68%，季減 5.75 個百分點，年減 1.74 個百分點，歸屬母公司稅後純益 6.32 億元，季減 85.5%，年減 35.29%，每股純益 0.66 元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臻鼎 - KY 並看好各類邊緣 AI 裝置需求增溫，包含 AI 手機、智慧眼鏡、人形機器人、智能車等，同時 AI 伺服器、光通訊與 IC 載板等高階產品新訂單陸續挹注。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
